# IAM RAG + deploy operating checklist

## Source law (non-negotiable)

- **Canonical:** Git, R2, D1 Layer 0, live provider/binding config
- **Derived mirrors:** Supabase pgvector + Cloudflare Vectorize â€” rebuildable search cache, not SSOT
- Skill: `skills/agentsam-vectorize-lanes/SKILL.md` Â· D1 rules: `rule_agentsam_vectorize_embed_pipeline`, `rule_vectorize_router`, `vectorize_dimension_integrity_rule`

## Before changing vector/RAG behavior

Inspect the lane contract: model, dims, Supabase table, Vectorize index/binding, R2/git source path, D1 receipt table, `workspace_id`.

## Before `npm run deploy:full`

1. `git status` â€” inneranimalmedia clean or intentionally scoped; **report** `iam-pwa-services` dirty files separately; never mix PWA signup/auth-proxy with vector/RAG commits
2. Migrations applied or explicitly deferred; repo migration files match prod
3. R2 skill/script uploads done when content changed
4. `node --check` on touched `.js` / `.mjs`
5. Optional (when search behavior changed): `./scripts/with-cloudflare-env.sh node scripts/verify-rag-ingest-protocol.mjs --require-fresh`

## Ingest / reindex protocol (scripts)

Shared lib: `scripts/lib/rag-ingest-protocol.mjs`

| Guard | Requirement |
|-------|-------------|
| Retry/backoff | OpenAI 503/429/502/504 and Vectorize transient errors â€” do not abort whole run |
| Hash skip | Skip unchanged content by `content_hash` |
| Receipts | D1 `vectorize_sync_log.details_json`: `run_id`, `git_commit_sha`, `workspace_id`, index, counts, status |
| Prune | After successful **full** run only: delete mirror rows + Vectorize ids for paths missing from approved source set (`--no-prune` to disable) |
| Index scope | Production `main` or explicit approved branch; skip build output, logs, cache, `node_modules`, WIP noise |
| Lane routing | One lane per job â€” CODE vs DOCUMENTS vs SCHEMA vs MEMORY vs MEDIA; no blind all-lane query |

Scripts: `reindex_codebase_dashboard_agent.mjs`, `ingest_r2_to_rag.mjs`, `ingest_repo_skills_rag.mjs`

## After deploy â€” verify (stop and report on failure)

1. `npm run deploy:full` completed successfully
2. Worker live (`curl /api/health` or dashboard load)
3. D1 migration state matches repo
4. `vectorize_sync_log` run receipts present when ingest/reindex ran
5. Services manifest reachable (PWA tier-1 when applicable)
6. Agent Sam answers a question using freshly indexed code/docs (manual smoke)

**Do not claim deploy/reindex success until receipts and smoke checks pass.**

## Do not bundle in deploy gate

- Full Playwright suite / multi-route smokes (unless user explicitly asks)
- Full reindex â€śjust becauseâ€ť â€” only when source set or lane contract changed
